flowchart TD
    A[任务 query] --> B[MemoryStore]
    B --> C[核心记忆全量读取]
    B --> D[FTS5 关键词召回]
    C --> E[按 id 合并去重]
    D --> E
    E --> F[过滤 rejected]
    F --> G[StalenessEngine 标记 stale/unconfirmed]
    G --> H{启用 token budget?}
    H -- 否 --> I[ContextInjectionResult]
    H -- 是 --> J[ContextBudgetManager]
    J --> K{protected 放得下?}
    K -- 否 --> X[ContextBudgetExceededError]
    K -- 是 --> I
